  <summary date="2019-02-14T15:29:27Z" status="Introduced in House">Lobbyist Loophole Closure Act

This bill broadens the scope of lobbying activities that trigger lobbyist registration and disclosure requirements.

Specifically, it expands lobbying activities to include legislative, political, and strategic counseling services.</summary>
